data.title: Best little cafe in Schenectady
data.text:
Great value; quick service; and very friendly owners who take prode in their business.
Daily food specials make this little breakfast / lunch spot a hidden gem in Schenectady

data.title: awesome place
data.text: the food is outstanding the staff is very fun energetic outgoing the portions are huge and the prices are not  everything comes out made to order  the food presentation is great  it always tastes perfect  ive never had a bad meal there  also the homemade brownies and cupcakes r also very very good  but again the portion is enough to have two meals out of it    i recommend this place for breakfast lunch and  would deff reccomend  it for dinner   but they close at 2  .  they also deliver  and take dine in orders  if your lookinf for a great homecooked meal  deannas is the place to go

data.title: basic breakfast place with friendly service
data.text:
very much a cafe and not a restaurant. Morning gets trade from regulars for coffee or work meetings over eggs. I liked the breakfast burrito.
Free internet and the owner very helpfully printed out a boarding pass for us on her computer.
